                        <p>Sri Krishnadevaraya University, Ananthapuramu, had its beginning as a Postgraduate Centre of Sri Venkateswara University in the year 1967-68. Fulfilling the desires of the people of the region, the Autonomous Postgraduate Centre was accorded the status of a University in the year 1981. Evolved over the decades and in 2015 SKU College has divided into two colleges of which SKU College of Sciences is one. SKU College of Sciences has 16 Departments offering 19 PG courses.</p>
